  <SourceScript>k__BackingField: "Narration: Welp. Another day another dollar.\r\n\r\nNarration:
    Maybe you\u2019re actually cut out for this.\r\n\r\nNarration: You didn\u2019t
    really like socializing before.\r\n\r\nNarration: But honestly\u2026 this isn\u2019t
    too bad.\r\n\r\nNarration: Its a shame that once you have your name back you\u2019re
    not really going to have enough money\u2026 or drive\u2026 to keep this going.\r\n\r\nNarration:
    After all\u2026 this kinda job seems like it would burn you out\u2026 right?\r\n\r\nNarration:
    You don\u2019t really know.\r\n\r\nNarration: Maybe sleeping on it will help\u2026\r\n"
